Cam::

She went to the energon synthesizer and made up a fresh bottle of 
energon for the baby.  She sat down on the floor and held the baby in 
her arms. She gently cradled the baby and gave her the bottle. "Well, 
I know you can't talk yet, but, well, when you can, you can call me 
Aunty Cam."  she said with a smile. She opened up her comlink to 
Windlord. "Hey, Windy, I still have the baby with me. Since I was 
taking care of the baby you you, can I go outside now and play? it's 
my turn to be the big bot and I wanna go and play. Pleeeeeeze?!" as 
she was feeding the baby.
